<style>
.page-hero {
  min-height: 42vh;
  display: flex;
  align-items: flex-end;
  justify-content: center;
  text-align: center;
  padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--gutter) var(--space-xl);
  position: relative;
  overflow: hidden;
  background-color: #060402;
  background-image:
    linear-gradient(180deg,
      rgba(2,1,0,0.72) 0%,
      rgba(4,2,1,0.50) 40%,
      rgba(2,1,0,0.80) 100%
    ),
    url({{ 'hero-bg.jpg' | asset_url }});
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: center 30%;
}

.page-hero__eyebrow {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.3em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--brass-mid, #8A6828);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

.page-hero__title {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(42px, 7vw, 96px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: #D4B896;
  line-height: 1.05;
  margin: 0;
}

.page-hero__title em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brass, #C8851A);
}

/* Brass rail divider */
.page-rail {
  height: 5px;
  background: linear-gradient(90deg,
    transparent 0%,
    #8B6914 5%,
    #C8851A 15%,
    #E8CC78 28%,
    #D4AE50 38%,
    #C8851A 50%,
    #E8CC78 62%,
    #D4AE50 72%,
    #C8851A 85%,
    #8B6914 95%,
    transparent 100%
  );
  box-shadow: 0 0 18px rgba(255,154,46,0.3);
}

/* Story body */
.page-body {
  max-width: 780px;
  margin: 0 auto;
  padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--gutter);
}

.page-body__section {
  margin-bottom: var(--space-2xl);
}

.page-body__section:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

.page-body__label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.28em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--brass, #C8851A);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
}

.page-body__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(26px, 3.5vw, 40px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cream, #F0E8D8);
  line-height: 1.15;
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.page-body__heading em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brass, #C8851A);
}

.page-body__text {
  font-family: var(--font-body, 'EB Garamond', serif);
  font-size: clamp(17px, 1.6vw, 20px);
  line-height: 1.75;
  color: var(--stone, #8A7A6A);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.page-body__text:last-child {
  margin-bottom: 0;
}

/* Pull quote */
.page-pull-quote {
  border-left: 3px solid var(--brass, #C8851A);
  padding: var(--space-md) var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-xl) 0;
  background: rgba(200,133,26,0.05);
}

.page-pull-quote p {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(20px, 2.5vw, 28px);
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--cream, #F0E8D8);
  line-height: 1.4;
  margin: 0;
}

/* Three pillars */
.page-pillars {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
  gap: var(--space-lg);
  margin: var(--space-2xl) 0;
  padding: var(--space-xl) 0;
  border-top: 1px solid rgba(200,133,26,0.12);
  border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(200,133,26,0.12);
}

.page-pillar__label {
  font-family: var(--font-ui);
  font-size: 9px;
  letter-spacing: 0.24em;
  text-transform: uppercase;
  color: var(--brass, #C8851A);
  display: block;
  margin-bottom: 10px;
}

.page-pillar__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(18px, 2vw, 22px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cream, #F0E8D8);
  margin-bottom: 8px;
}

.page-pillar__text {
  font-size: 14px;
  color: var(--stone, #8A7A6A);
  line-height: 1.65;
}

/* CTA strip */
.page-cta {
  text-align: center;
  padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--gutter);
  background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(200,133,26,0.04) 50%, transparent 100%);
}

.page-cta__heading {
  font-family: var(--font-display);
  font-size: clamp(28px, 4vw, 48px);
  font-weight: 700;
  color: var(--cream, #F0E8D8);
  margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
}

.page-cta__heading em {
  font-style: italic;
  color: var(--brass, #C8851A);
}

@media (max-width: 700px) {
  .page-pillars { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: var(--space-md); }
  .page-body { padding: var(--space-xl) var(--gutter-sm); }
}
</style>

<!-- Hero -->
<div class="page-hero">
  <div>
    <p class="page-hero__eyebrow">Dark &amp; Diffused · Est. 2025 · Australia</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title">The Story Behind<br><em>the atmosphere.</em></h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="page-rail"></div>

<!-- Body -->
<div class="page-body">

  <div class="page-body__section">
    <span class="page-body__label">The Problem</span>
    <h2 class="page-body__heading">The market forgot <em>the man.</em></h2>
    <p class="page-body__text">
      Scent is one of the most powerful forces a human being has access to. It rewires your mood before you've even noticed it happened. It pulls memories out of thin air. It changes the energy of a room, shifts the attention of everyone who walks into it, and quietly signals exactly who you are — without you saying a word.
    </p>
    <p class="page-body__text">
      Men know this. Increasingly, men care deeply about the spaces they inhabit — the way a room feels, the way it looks, the way it smells. But when it came to diffusers, the market had one answer: flowers, pastels, and apology.
    </p>
    <p class="page-body__text">
      Nothing built for the man who wants oud and cedarwood. Nothing designed for a desk that means business. Nothing that looks like it belongs next to a glass of whisky.
    </p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-pull-quote">
    <p>"I wanted a product I couldn't find anywhere. So I built the place to find it."</p>
  </div>

  <div class="page-body__section">
    <span class="page-body__label">The Mission</span>
    <h2 class="page-body__heading">Atmosphere is not <em>an accident.</em></h2>
    <p class="page-body__text">
      Dark &amp; Diffused exists for men who curate their environments with the same precision they apply to everything else. The ones who understand that the details — the lighting, the texture, the scent drifting across the room — are not afterthoughts. They are the statement.
    </p>
    <p class="page-body__text">
      Every diffuser we carry was chosen because it does something. The steam that curls and shifts like smoke from a fire. The glow that changes the temperature of a room. The scent that makes people stop and ask what that is. We're not selling air fresheners. We're selling the tools to own your atmosphere.
    </p>
  </div>

</div>

<!-- Three pillars -->
<div style="max-width: 1080px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 0 var(--gutter);">
  <div class="page-pillars">
    <div class="page-pillar">
      <span class="page-pillar__label">Sensory</span>
      <div class="page-pillar__heading">Steam. Glow. Scent.</div>
      <p class="page-pillar__text">Three layers working at once. The visual theatre of vapour in motion. The warmth of ambient light. And the scent that does the heavy lifting on mood and memory.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="page-pillar">
      <span class="page-pillar__label">Masculine</span>
      <div class="page-pillar__heading">Built for men.</div>
      <p class="page-pillar__text">Dark finishes. Industrial forms. Scents that command — not apologise. Every product chosen because it looks right in a man's space and performs the way a man expects.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="page-pillar">
      <span class="page-pillar__label">Deliberate</span>
      <div class="page-pillar__heading">Chosen with intent.</div>
      <p class="page-pillar__text">We don't carry everything. We carry what earns its place. Each diffuser, each scent — selected because it raises the bar on what a room can feel like.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- CTA -->
<div class="page-cta">
  <h2 class="page-cta__heading">Ready to own <em>the room?</em></h2>
  <a href="/collections/all" class="btn-brass" style="margin-top: var(--space-md); display: inline-flex;">Enter the Bar</a>
</div>

